    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-quality 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the high-revving S54 powerplant, characterized by its cast-iron block and six individual throttle bodies. The mechanical synchronization of the double-VANOS variable valve timing is flawless, and the rod bearings have been proactively addressed. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, housing a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission that shifts with surgical precision. Riding on OEM Style 67 forged wheels, the suspension remains tight with no bushing deflection. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
